  "1862950": {
    "name": "苏打队长",
    "steam_appid": 1862950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/1dce74824154b72d24e94a6300436d63.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=387 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变身为你心目中的终极苏打英雄，用闪闪发光的苏打 “武气” 消灭外星军队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苏打队长》将平台射击游戏带到了新高峰。游戏让你品尝使用各种各类含有独特能力的苏打水和华丽的 “武气”挑战强大和令人心跳加速的敌人。 陶醉在流畅的物体控制中，让你在消灭敌人和穿越混乱中时随意地摇晃、晃动和叮当作响。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 “泡沫充风枪” 和 “瓶装发射气” 等 “武气” 击落一波又一波的贪财外星人。 在Aleix Ramon的创作乐曲中选择您最喜欢的气泡水和水枪来取得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/2375bde1267b362312490009e62e3710.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/2375bde1267b362312490009e62e3710.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/2375bde1267b362312490009e62e3710.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>给自己的野心解渴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种近程、远程和近战“武气”来消灭外星入侵者。 扔“手榴罐”、用苏打喷气背包、或整台自动售货机将它们压扁！ 磨练你的技能来躲避并击败 18 种不同类型的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/790df91494be06cb900dccec562b7146.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/790df91494be06cb900dccec562b7146.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/790df91494be06cb900dccec562b7146.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>混合、搭配和升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演不同的苏打英雄，像柠檬汁挥官或抹茶珍珠奶少微，让敌人眼花缭乱。 获取超过 14 种配件和升级品，例如 气泡跑步靴和泡腾翅膀，以适应您的游戏风格并增强您的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/fed6e697479e206a2968d053243a8ed9.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/fed6e697479e206a2968d053243a8ed9.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/fed6e697479e206a2968d053243a8ed9.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>紧张刺激的战役</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满活力的故事模式中射击和炸毁外心入侵者，穿越三种具有不同气泡主题的神秘区域。 体验多过60个不同的可选任务，追击敌人，解锁物品商店并探索秘密升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/5cb39224cc2fa8923e3a2c7912bcc99a.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/5cb39224cc2fa8923e3a2c7912bcc99a.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/5cb39224cc2fa8923e3a2c7912bcc99a.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>永无休止的无尽模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无尽模式中与永无休止的敌人战斗，每一关都比上一关更加激烈！ 你能在外星人的攻击中幸存下来并在全球排行榜上获得令人瞠目结舌的高分吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/6906999d91479466d3cb72b806f299c2.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/6906999d91479466d3cb72b806f299c2.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/6906999d91479466d3cb72b806f299c2.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>带有苏打精神的继承者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到《Super Crate Box》的启发，《苏打船长》通过完善的故事模式、视觉效果、敌人、机制、以及可定制的武器装载，提升这一类型的激烈且基于技能的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/805d7f8d7ba253dbd061ad1195079968.poster.avif?t=1770937991\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/805d7f8d7ba253dbd061ad1195079968.webm?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862950/extras/805d7f8d7ba253dbd061ad1195079968.mp4?t=1770937991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>大小适合的乐趣</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苏打船长》含有一系列难度选择，适合初级玩家、经验丰富的家和速跑者。 根据您的喜好调整设置和选项，例如瞄准辅助、敌人移动速度和色盲模式，以获得优化且愉快的游戏体验。</p>",
